This specifies the data fields in tidy data.txt

Identifiers are subject and activity

The measurements which were taken are as follows:

1. Features
2. Activities
3.Subject_test
4.x_test
5.y_test
6.subject_train
7.x_train
8.y_train


The train and the test data were binded together using the rbind function and merged with Subject.

The messy data was turned into Tidy data using the Tidy data package and variables containing mean and standard deviation variables were selected

The variables of the tidy data frame was changed to a more understandable format and mean and standard deviation were computed for respective columns

The final data frame was written into FinalData.txt file. 
